%20employees%20to%20use%20makeshift%20solutions%20that%20are%20neither%20sanitary%20nor%20adequate%20for%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20these%20allegations%2C%20an%20Amazon%20India%20spokesperson%20stated%20that%20the%20company%20takes%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20its%20employees%20seriously.%20They%20mentioned%20the%20presence%20of%20heat%20index%20monitoring%20devices%20and%20cooling%20measures%20in%20their%20facilities%2C%20asserting%20that%20employees%20are%20provided%20with%20adequate%20water%2C%20hydration%20breaks%2C%20and%20rest%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20isn't%20confined%20to%20India%20alone.%20Amazon%20has%20faced%20similar%20allegations%20internationally%2C%20with%20authorities%20in%20the%20US%20citing%20safety%20violations%20and%20ergonomic%20hazards%20in%20several%20warehouses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20company%20fired%20a%20warehouse%20worker%20in%20US%20after%20he%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20TikTok%20about%20having%20to%20pick%20up%20heavy%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20female%20marketing%20managers%20in%20Seattle%20have%20also%20filed%20a%20proposed%20class%20action%20accusing%20Amazon%20of%20widespread%20sex%20discrimination%20and%20that%20the%20tech%20giant%20has%20retaliated%20against%20them%2C%20including%20by%20firing%20one%20and%20forcing%20another%20to%20quit.%20The%20workers%20in%20an%20amended%20complaint%20claim%20Amazon's%20illegal%20conduct%20only%20escalated%20in%20the%20weeks%20after%20they%20initially%20filed%20the%20lawsuit%20in%20November%20last%20year%20alleging%20violations%20of%20federal%20and%20Washington%20state%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718427060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Faf2hvcs4_amazon-india-worker_625x300_15_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famazon-india-workers-get-no-toilet-water-breaks-till-task-is-done-report-5894255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amazon%20India%20finds%20itself%20under%20scrutiny%20after%20allegations%20of%20harsh%20working%20conditions%20and%20stringent%20productivity%20demands%20surfaced%20from%20workers%20at%20its%20warehouses%20in%20Haryana's%20industrial%20hub%20of%20Manesar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famazon-india-workers-get-no-toilet-water-breaks-till-task-is-done-report-5894255%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famazon-india-workers-get-no-toilet-water-breaks-till-task-is-done-report-5894255%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famazon-india-workers-get-no-toilet-water-breaks-till-task-is-done-report-5894255%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Physics%20Wallah%20CEO%20Moves%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Seeks%20Probe%20Into%20NEET%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAlakh%20Pandey%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20prominent%20EdTech%20firm%20Physics%20Wallah%2C%20has%20petitioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20surrounding%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20examination.%20This%20national-level%20entrance%20test%2C%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20and%20crucial%20for%20admissions%20into%20MBBS%20and%20other%20medical%20courses%2C%20has%20been%20embroiled%20in%20controversy%20over%20alleged%20irregularities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandey's%20petition%20claims%20the%20alleged%20arbitrary%20awarding%20of%20grace%20marks%20to%20over%201%2C500%20candidates%20by%20the%20NTA.%20He%20has%20requested%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20establish%20an%20expert%20panel%20to%20scrutinise%20the%20examination%20process%20and%20its%20results.%20The%20NEET-UG%202024%2C%20held%20on%20May%205%20across%204%2C750%20centres%2C%20saw%20participation%20from%20approximately%2024%20lakh%20candidates.%20While%20results%20were%20anticipated%20on%20June%2014%2C%20they%20were%20announced%20early%20on%20June%204%2C%20allegedly%20due%20to%20expedited%20answer%20sheet%20evaluations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EControversy%20erupted%20following%20allegations%20of%20question%20paper%20leaks%20and%20the%20granting%20of%20grace%20marks%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20protests%20and%20legal%20challenges%20in%20seven%20high%20courts%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20unprecedented%20performance%2C%20with%2067%20students%20scoring%20a%20perfect%20720%20-%20including%20six%20from%20a%20single%20centre%20in%20Haryana's%20Faridabad%20-%20has%20raised%20suspicions%20of%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2010%2C%20students%20gathered%20in%20Delhi%2C%20demanding%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20these%20allegations.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20contentious%20grace%20marks%20may%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20unusually%20high%20number%20of%20top%20scorers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-UG%20examination%2C%20overseen%20by%20the%20NTA%2C%20is%20a%20gateway%20for%20medical%20admissions%20in%20both%20government%20and%20private%20institutions%20across%20India.%20However%2C%20the%20integrity%20of%20this%20year's%20process%20has%20been%20called%20into%20question%2C%20prompting%20protests%20and%20legal%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20uproar%2C%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20assured%20aspirants%20and%20parents%20that%20there%20is%20no%20substantial%20evidence%20of%20a%20paper%20leak.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20allegations%20are%20under%20investigation%20by%20competent%20authorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20evidence%20of%20any%20paper%20leak%20yet.%20There%20are%20allegations%20and%20competent%20authorities%20are%20looking%20into%20them.%20Certain%20allegations%20and%20loose%20information%20are%20coming%20in.%20Let%20us%20wait%20for%20the%20probe%20by%20the%20authorities%20concerned.%20Let's%20wait%20till%20July%208%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20judgment.%20There's%20nothing%20to%20hide...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pradhan%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20reassured%20students%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20delivered%20a%20judgment%20on%20the%20issue.%20He%20announced%20that%20all%201%2C563%20affected%20students%20would%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20reappear%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20especially%20those%20from%20the%20six%20centres%20where%20time%20constraints%20were%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20measures%2C%20questions%20remain%20about%20the%20NTA's%20response%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20intervention.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20not%20true.%20After%20the%20anomaly%20came%20to%20light%2C%20the%20NTA%20came%20up%20with%20a%20formula%20-%20the%20grace%20mark%20formula.%20It%20was%20cited%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20well.%20However%2C%20some%20anomalies%20were%20found%20in%20that%20formula%20because%20six%20students%20became%20the%20highest%20scorers%20on%20the%20list.%20That%20was%20an%20eyesore%20for%20many%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20delegation%20of%20students%20and%20parents%20met%20with%20Mr%20Pradhan%2C%20who%20urged%20them%20to%20trust%20the%20government's%20intentions%20and%20efforts%20to%20rectify%20the%20situation.%20He%20dismissed%20calls%20to%20scrap%20the%20NEET%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20entrance%20exam%20remains%20a%20fair%20metric%2C%20citing%20last%20year's%20top%20performer%20from%20a%20rural%20Tamil%20Nadu%20state%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718426880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fif3kku1g_physics-wallah-alakh-pandey-_625x300_15_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fphysics-wallah-ceo-alakh-pandey-wants-expert-panel-to-probe-neet-row-5894328%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alakh%20Pandey%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20prominent%20EdTec