3B%20however%2C%20it%20became%20the%20biggest%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20those%20who%20had%20no%20faith%20in%20Ram%20were%20stopped%20at%20234%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20%26quot%3BSee%20the%20'Vidhan'%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20in%20democracy%3B%20those%20who%20did%20'Bhakti'%20of%20Ram%2C%20but%20gradually%20turned%20arrogant%2C%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20party%3B%20however%2C%20the%20vote%20and%20the%20power%20that%20they%20should%20have%20been%20given%20was%20stopped%20by%20God%20due%20to%20arrogance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20remarks%20sparked%20a%20row.%20The%20RSS%20leader%20sought%20to%20mitigate%20the%20damage%20by%20clarifying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20mood%20of%20the%20country%20is%20very%20clear%20at%20present.%20Those%20who%20opposed%20Lord%20Ram%20are%20not%20in%20power%3B%20those%20who%20set%20the%20goal%20to%20respect%20Lord%20Ram%20are%20in%20power%20and%20the%20government%20has%20been%20formed%20for%20the%20third%20time%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20remarks%20follow%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat's%20statement%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20had%20said%20that%20a%20true%20'sevak'%20should%20serve%20people%20without%20arrogance%20and%20maintain%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20yesterday%20sought%20to%20quell%20the%20suggestions%20of%20a%20rift%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20that%20Mohan%20Bhagwat's%20recent%20critical%20references%20related%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20were%20aimed%20at%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20insisting%20that%20such%20claims%20are%20just%20speculation%20meant%20to%20create%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20rift%20between%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20RSS%20sources%20said%2C%20amid%20assertions%20by%20a%20section%20of%20people%2C%20including%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20that%20Mr%20Bhagwat's%20remarks%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Btrue%20sevak%20is%20never%20arrogant%2C%26quot%3B%20were%20a%20message%20to%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20following%20its%20below-par%20performance%20in%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20not%20much%20difference%20in%20his%20(Mr%20Bhagwat's)%20speech%20from%20what%20he%20had%20given%20after%20the%202014%20and%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Any%20address%20is%20bound%20to%20make%20a%20reference%20to%20an%20event%20as%20important%20as%20national%20elections.%20But%20it%20was%20misinterpreted%20and%20taken%20out%20of%20context%20to%20create%20confusion.%20His%20'arrogance'%20remark%20was%20never%20directed%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20or%20any%20BJP%20leader%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20had%20on%20Monday%20expressed%20concern%20over%20peace%20eluding%20Manipur%20even%20after%20one%20year%20of%20conflict%2C%20criticised%20the%20common%20discourse%20during%20polls%2C%20and%20called%20for%20moving%20on%20instead%20of%20unnecessary%20discussion%20on%20the%20what%20and%20how%20of%20the%20elections%20after%20they%20were%20over%20and%20results%20were%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20had%20seized%20on%20his%20remarks%20to%20take%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20BJP%20and%20PM%20Modi.%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20not%20the%20'one-third'%20Prime%20Minister's%20conscience%20or%20the%20repeated%20demands%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%2C%20perhaps%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20can%20prevail%20upon%20the%20former%20RSS%20office-bearer%20to%20go%20to%20Manipur.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20claims%20by%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20nothing%20but%20politics%20meant%20to%20spread%20confusion%2C%20the%20RSS%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718424960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fimn43fvo_rss-leader-in