is%20year.%20The%20group's%20name%20references%20%26quot%3BTzav-8%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20emergency%20call-up%20order%20for%20Israeli%20military%20reservists.%20It%20was%20formed%20by%20Israeli%20settlers%2C%20army%20reservists%2C%20and%20families%20of%20those%20taken%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20during%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20last%20year.%20These%20individuals%20oppose%20the%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Gaza%2C%20believing%20that%20much%20of%20the%20aid%20is%20diverted%20to%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20formation%2C%20Tsav%209%20has%20been%20implicated%20in%20numerous%20violent%20activities%20aimed%20at%20disrupting%20aid%20shipments%20to%20Gaza.%20The%20group's%20tactics%20include%20blockading%20roads%2C%20harassing%20drivers%2C%20and%20vandalising%20trucks.%20They%20have%20attacked%20convoys%20at%20the%20Kerem%20Shalom%20crossing%2C%20setting%20trucks%20on%20fire%2C%20and%20injuring%20both%20drivers%20and%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fpmeu4bc8_tsav-9_625x300_15_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Reuters%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Tsav%209%20members%20looted%20and%20burned%20two%20aid%20trucks%20near%20Hebron%2C%20an%20act%20that%20was%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20campaign%20to%20prevent%20essential%20supplies%20from%20reaching%20Gaza.%20Footage%20has%20surfaced%20showing%20the%20group%20ransacking%20aid%20shipments%2C%20dumping%20food%20and%20medical%20supplies%20onto%20the%20road.%20These%20actions%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20worsening%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20famine%20conditions%20have%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3