2%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc25524gxlgno%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20the%20US%20celebrities%20were%20Whoopi%20Goldberg%2C%20Stephen%20Colbert%2C%20Chris%20Rock%20and%20Jimmy%20Fallon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc25524gxlgno%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22King%20Charles'%20birthday%20isn't%20until%20November.%20So%20why%20is%20it%20being%20celebrated%20in%20the%20summer%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20royal%20family%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666868ed764df161125881cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20royal%20family%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%202023.%3Cp%3ESamir%20Hussein%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrooping%20the%20Colour%202024%20will%20take%20place%20in%20London%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20annual%20military%20parade%20serves%20as%20King%20Charles%20III's%20official%20birthday%20celebration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20royal%20family%20will%20gather%20on%20the%20balcony%20of%20Buckingham%20Palace%20to%20mark%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fking-charles-iii-reign-so-far-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKing%20Charles%20III%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20born%20on%20November%2014%2C%201948%2C%20so%20you%20likely%20wouldn't%20expect%20him%20to%20be%20thinking%20about%20his%20birthday%20in%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20thousands%20will%20celebrate%20the%20king's%20birthday%20in%20the%20UK%20on%20Saturday%20at%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20royal%20events%20of%20the%20year%3A%20Trooping%20the%20Colour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royal.uk%2Fwhat-is-trooping-the-colour%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroyal%20family's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%20has%20been%20the%20British%20sovereign's%20official%20birthday%20celebration%20for%20over%20260%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20is%20marked%20with%20a%20parade%20and%20massive%20fanfare%20in%20June%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2ebe6b6-d3e9-469f-afdf-56831a491a0d%5C%22%3ETrooping%20the%20Colour%20is%20the%20monarch's%20official%20birthday%20celebration%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20celebration%20occurs%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20regardless%20of%20when%20the%20reigning%20monarch's%20actual%20birthday%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22King%20Charles%20and%20Queen%20Camilla%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666866d7764df161125880cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKing%20Charles%20and%20Queen%20Camilla%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%202023.%3Cp%3EChris%20Jackson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royal.uk%2Fqueens-birthday%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroyal%20family's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20that%20the%20chance%20of%20the%20weather%20being%20suitable%20for%20outdoor%20activities%20is%20higher%20in%20May%20or%20June.%20Considering%20much%20of%20the%20event%20takes%20place%20outside%2C%20scheduling%20it%20for%20the%20summer%20is%20easier.%20Nowadays%2C%20the%20event%20typically%20takes%20place%20on%20a%20Saturday%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2Fnews%2Fwhy-do-british-monarchs-have-two-birthdays%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHistory%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20King%20George%20II%20was%20the%20first%20monarch%20to%20move%20his%20birthday%20pageantry%20to%20the%20summer%2C%20as%20he%20was%20born%20in%20October%2C%20but%20he%20combined%20his%20official%20celebration%20with%20a%20summer%20military%20parade%20in%201748.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20monarch's%20actual%20birthday%20is%20publicly%20acknowledged%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royal.uk%2Fgun-salutes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20royal%20gun%20salute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20sovereign%20typically%20celebrates%20privately%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2fa182e-7e24-44b0-8cdf-50c04b881a16%5C%22%3EA%20military%20parade%20is%20the%20centerpiece%20of%20the%20event%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%2C%20a%20parade%20of%20royals%20and%20military%20personnel%20travels%20from%20Buckingham%20Palace%20to%20the%20Horse%20Guards%20Parade%20at%20Whitehall%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20royal%20family's%20website%20states%20that%20the%20parade%20includes%20over%201%2C400%20soldiers%2C%20400%20musicians%2C%20and%20200%20horses%2C%20and%20the%20royals%20typically%20ride%20on%20horseback%20or%20in%20carriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20monarch%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20event%20from%20either%20carriage%20or%20horseback.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnewsround%2F43794588%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%20rode%20a%20horse%20during%20the%20parade%20until%201987.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queen%20Elizabeth%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%201985.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66686582ed9a404d829c67e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQueen%20Elizabeth%20at%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%201985.%3Cp%3EAnwar%20Hussein%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20parade%20reaches%20Whitehall%2C%20the%20monarch%20formally%20inspects%20the%20troops%20during%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20the%20chosen%20Regimental%20Colour%2C%20or%20flag%2C%20is%20carried%20through%20the%20ranks%20of%20participating%20soldiers%20before%20they%20march%20back%20to%20Buckingham%20Palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20onlookers%20cheer%20on%20the%20participants%20as%20they%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F1034322%2F20210713-FOI2021_06427_redacted_response_Redacted.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20FOIA%20request%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20the%202021%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%20cost%2059%2C662%20pounds%2C%20which%20would%20be%20approximately%20%2475%2C604%20today.%20That%20total%20includes%20stable%20costs%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20fuel%2C%20among%20other%20fees%2C%20though%20it%20does%20not%20factor%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20police%20presence%20required%20to%20keep%20the%20event%20safe%20for%20the%20royals%20and%20attendees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c860c09-d877-4936-a474-2eab118d03fe%5C%22%3ETrooping%20the%20Colour%20brings%20the%20royal%20family%20together%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrooping%20the%20Colour%20culminates%20in%20a%20flypast%20by%20RAF%20pilots%20over%20Buckingham%20Palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flyover%20is%20arguably%20the%20most%20iconic%20moment%20of%20the%20event%2C%20as%20the%20royal%20family%20watches%20the%20planes%20go%20by%20from%20Buckingham%20Palace's%20balcony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrooping%20the%20Colour%20marks%20one%20of%20the%20few%20times%20a%20year%20the%20royal%20family%20gathers%20in%20one%20place%2C%20so%20they%20are%20always%20heavily%20photographed%20when%20they%20appear%20on%20the%20balcony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20occasion%20offers%20a%20chance%20to%20see%20how%20royals%20interact%20with%20each%20other%2C%20with%20people%20analyzing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrooping-the-colour-buck