work%20by%20buying%20adjacent%20properties%20in%202018%20and%202019%20for%20%2459%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20compound%20will%20include%C2%A0a%20bunkhouse%2C%20a%20guesthouse%2C%20and%20a%20gym%2C%20per%20documents%20seen%20by%20SFGate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20people%20have%20been%20wondering%20what%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20is%20up%20to%20in%20Lake%20Tahoe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20our%20first%20clue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Meta%20CEO%20plans%20to%20build%20a%2075%2C000-square-foot%2C%20seven-building%20compound%20on%20the%20lake's%20western%20shore%2C%20according%20to%20planning%20documents%20seen%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfgate.com%2Frenotahoe%2Farticle%2Fmark-zuckerberg-lake-tahoe-compound-19513352.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20news%20site%20SFGate%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20started%20to%20lay%20the%20groundwork%20in%20December%202018%2C%20when%20he%20bought%20a%203.5-acre%20property%20from%20the%20family%20of%20the%20late%20investment%20banker%20Robert%20Quist%20for%20%2422%20million.%20The%20next%20month%2C%20he%20bought%20another%20estate%20next%20door%20for%20%2437%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Quist%20spread%2C%20also%20called%20the%20Carousel%20Estate%2C%20included%20a%20pier%20suitable%20for%20a%20large%20yacht%20and%20a%20house%20with%20seven%20bedrooms%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Funraveling-mark-zuckerbergs-secret-deal-for-a-59-million-tahoe-compound-11556811876%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20cited%20Zillow.%20The%20property%20next%20door%2C%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-mark-zuckerberg-secret-lake-tahoe-estate-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Brushwood%20Estate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20a%20house%20with%20six%20bedrooms%2C%20five%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20two%20half-baths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E