m%20my%20previous%20model%2C%20which%20smells%20heavily%20of%20the%20dog%20when%20it%20empties%20into%20the%20bin.)%20Then%2C%20I%20allowed%20the%20vacuum%20to%20charge%20before%20setting%20it%20loose.%20The%20app%20was%20an%20easy%20setup%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20QR%20code%20on%20the%20base.%20However%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20it%20performed%20on%20its%20own.%20Simply%20download%2C%20add%20the%20vacuum%2C%20and%20follow%20the%20step-by-step%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20already%20had%20a%20Shark%20logged%20into%20their%20app%20system%2C%20there%20was%20zero%20setup%20here.%20However%2C%20the%20Shark%20app%20is%20intuitive%2C%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20and%20quickly%20gets%20a%20floor%20plan%20of%20your%20house.%20You%20can%20also%20create%20no-go%20zones%20(that%20you%20can%20turn%20on%2Foff)%2C%20which%20is%20ideal%20for%20keeping%20your%20vacuum%20on%20the%20move.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20closed%20off%20our%20mudroom%2C%20which%20is%20full%20of%2C%20well%2C%20junk.%20I%20often%20close%20my%20kids'%20rooms%20before%20they're%20cleaned%2C%20too.%20The%20app%20can%20allow%20you%20to%20start%2Fstop%20the%20vacuum%20while%20away%20from%20home%2C%20too%2C%20in%20case%20you%20forgot%20to%20start%20it%20or%20are%20having%20last-minute%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewcomers%20will%20find%20an%20easy%20learning%20curve%20simply%20by%20following%20the%20steps%20the%20app%20prompts%20them%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Shark%20vacuum%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Shark%20vacuum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Red%20lights%20flash%20on%20the%20Shark%20Detect%20Pro%20to%20avoid%20large%20objects%20or%20hitting%20walls%2C%20etc.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554fe0122cf74a57397da25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shark%20Detect%20Pro%20easily%20traverses%20carpet%2C%20and%20uses%20a%20combination%20of%20scanning%20lasers%20and%203D%20to%20navigate.%3Cp%3EBethaney%20Phillips%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20vacuum%20was%20charged%2C%20I%20hit%20%26quot%3Bclean%26quot%3B%20and%20watched%20it%20roll.%20Surprisingly%2C%20yet%20not%20surprisingly%2C%20based%20on%20all%20of%20the%20new%20and%20patented%20tech%2C%20the%20vacuum%20was%20much%20more%20controlled%20than%20its%20predecessors.%20With%20two%20scanning%20lasers%20and%203D%20mapping%20plotting%20out%20each%20move%2C%20the%20Detect%20Pro%20seemingly%20knew%20where%20every%20wall%2C%20ledge%2C%20or%20large%20piece%20of%20crumb%20was%20while%20still%20inches%20away.%20This%20is%20different%20from%20other%20brands%20that%20incorporate%20cameras%20into%20their%20technology%2C%20while%20LIDAR%20provides%20privacy.%20It%20turned%20on%20a%20dime%2C%20avoiding%20walls%20and%20edges%20alike%2C%20and%20just%20like%20it%20promised%2C%20it%20didn't%20get%20stuck.%20I%20left%20out%20some%20Nerf%20darts%20and%20LEGOs%20on%20purpose%20%E2%80%93%20what%20our%20old%20model%20commonly%20choked%20on%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20Detect%20Pro%20simply%20avoided%20them.%20Amazing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20of%20the%20Shark%20Detect%20Pro%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20the%20wheels.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554fe014ca513d82429f5b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20vacuum's%20wheels%20have%20a%20big%20tread%20and%20are%20able%20to%20rise%2Fsink%20back%20into%20the%20model%20to%20avoid%20getting%20stuck.%20These%20features%20are%20key%20in%20its%20never-stuck%20capabilities.%3Cp%3EBethaney%20Phillips%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20combo%20of%20DirtDetect%20Technology%2C%20FloorDetect%E2%84%A2%20Technology%2C%20EdgeDetect%20Technology%2C%20NeverStuck%20Technology%E2%84%A2%20it's%20safe%20to%20say%20this%20vacuum%20has%20a%20lot%20going%20on.%20In%20layman's%20terms%3A%20it%20finds%20the%20dirt%2C%20it%20knows%20and%20adjusts%20to%20the%20type%20of%20flooring%20it's%20on%20at%20the%20time%2C%20it%20senses%20and%20avoids%20edges%2C%20and%20it%20avoids%20large%20objects%20or%20flooring%20that%20could%20keep%20it%20from%20getting%20stuck.%20They%20covered%20a%20lot%20of%20bases%20with%20these%20new%20capabilities%2C%20that's%20for%20sure.%20It%20was%20especially%20telling%20to%20do%20a%20side-by-side%20with%20an%20older%20Shark%20model%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Detect%20Pro%20clearly%20lived%20up%20to%20its%20new%20capabilities'%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Shark%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655504e636d588dc55d0f515%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shark%20app%20creates%20a%20floorplan%20of%20your%20home%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20set%20boundaries%2C%20clean%20by%20room%2C%20schedule%20cleaning%20and%20review%20its%20cleaning%20paths.%3Cp%3EBethaney%20Phillips%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApp%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Detect%20Pro's%20app%20connects%20to%20the%20same%20Shark%20App%20that%20it%20uses%20for%20all%20of%20its%20vacuums.%20No%20complaints%20here%2C%20but%20it's%20nothing%20extraordinary.%20You%20can%20schedule%20cleaning%2C%20block%20off%20areas%20of%20the%20house%2C%20etc.%20After%20cleaning%2C%20you%20can%20review%20to%20see%20what%20spaces%20were%20covered%20in%20the%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20Use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Because%20I%20was%20already%20familiar%20with%20setting%20up%20a%20Shark%20Robot%20Vacuum%2C%20this%20thing%20was%20a%20breeze.%20However%2C%20it%20did%20offer%20less%20setup%20than%20previous%20models.%20Aside%20from%20the%20Odor%20Neutralizer%20puck%20filter%2C%20which%20simply%20screwed%20into%20the%20dust%20bin%2C%20the%20only%20set%20up%20was%20a%20snap-on%20brush.%20Even%20the%20dust%20bin%20was%20foolproof%2C%20needing%20to%20be%20plugged%20in.%20Once%20ready%2C%20the%20vacuum%20essentially%20runs%20itself.%20There%20is%20no%20hunting%20it%20down%20with%20errors%20or%20having%20to%20fish%20out%20rubber%20bands%20or%20pencil%20pieces%2C%20it%20just%20cleans.%20It%20will%20also%20self-empty%20and%20keep%20running%20(on%20new%20areas)%20until%20you%20tell%20it%20not%20to.%20Truly%20self-automated%2C%20without%20having%20to%20hunt%20it%20down%20stuck%20or%20dead%20somewhere%20in%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shark%20detect%20pro%20cleans%20flour%20on%20hardwood%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554fe024ca513d82429f5b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shark%20Detect%20Pro%20in%20Dirt%20Detect%20mode%20(purple%2Fblue%20light%20vs.%20green)%20to%20pick%20up%20flour.%20It%20was%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20most%20of%20the%20mess%2C%20aside%20from%20the%20residue%20it%20left%20from%20its%20own%20wheels%2Fbrush.%3Cp%3EBethaney%20Phillips%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%20Performance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Considering%20I%20regularly%20run%20my%20vacuum%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20much%20dirt%20it%20picked%20up%20and%20how%20frequently%20it%20emptied.%20In%20theory%2C%20the%20Detect%20Pro%20can%20tell%20where%20the%20dirt%20is%20hiding%2C%20so%20perhaps%20this%20was%20due%20to%20its%20tech%20that%20magnifies%20the%20mess.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20it%20picked%20up%20loads%20of%20dust%2C%20dirt%2C%20and%20pet%20hair.%20Unlike%20my%20other%20robot%2C%20though%2C%20it%20didn't%20choke%20on%20said%20pet%20hair.%20I%20would%20regularly%20have%20to%20disassemble%20to%20pull%20out%20the%20clogs.%20While%20the%20Detect%20Pro%20grabbed%20and%20emptied%20piles%20of%20pet%20hair%20while%20I%20was%20none-the-wiser.%20I%20even%20placed%20it%20on%20the%20dog%20bed%20to%20see%20what%20it%20could%20do%2C%20no%20spurting%20and%20no%2C%20it%20didn't%20get%20stuck%2C%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20running%20the%20Shark%20Detect%20Pro%20Robot%20Vacuum%20at%20least%20once%20a%20day%20and%20it%20has%20cut%20down%20on%20dirt%20and%20pet%20hair%20alike.%20I%20no%20longer%20see%20stray%20dust%20bunnies%20or%20fur%20balls%20hidden%20behind%20the%20furniture.%20I've%20also%20gained%20back%20time%20as%20it%20runs%20on%20its%20own%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20track%20down%20and%20rescue%20the%20vacuum%20just%20so%20it%20can%20continue%20working.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20house%20has%20both%20carpet%20and%20hardwood%2C%20as%20well%20as%20rugs.%20The%20vacuum%20lifts%20itself%20by%20its%20wheels%20to%20adjust%20for%20each%20surface.%20Suction%20also%20automatically%20adjusts%20on%20floor%20types%2C%20changing%20frequency%20when%20going%20from%20one%20to%20the%20other.%20It%20picked%20up%20equally%20well%20on%20both%20surfaces.%20However%2C%20it%20struggled%20on%20a%20shag%20carpet%20rug%2C%20spitting%20out%20Cheerios%20to%20avoid%20clogging.%20When%20finding%20a%20mess%2C%20the%20DirtDetect%20kicked%20into%20gear%2C%20changing%20tones%2C%20and%20the%20light%20on%20the%20vacuum%20went%20from%20green%20to%20purple%2Fblue.%20The%20vacuum%20then%20hovered%20in%20the%20area%2C%20grabbing%20as%20much%20dirt%20as%20possible%20before%20switching%20back%20to%20green%20mode%20and%20onto%20a%20new%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Shark%20Detect%20Pro's%20odor%20neutralizing%20puck.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554fe0122cf74a57397da27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shark%20Detect%20odor%20neutralizer%20technology%20snaps%20into%20the%20auto-empty%20base.