hich%20you%20can%20also%20get%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-1015-20%26h%3Dece887a1cc056071cacf8e0f0fa8ebbb74513a7ba4779c64d1cb1b0f89e8b689%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42cb4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fnaked-wines-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fus.nakedwines.com%252Fimpact12pk%253Firclickid%253DQSXxuVT9cxyPTVcw6R3znwhNUkHwpfzYeWegyM0%2526utm_source%253D196318%2526utm_content%253DBusiness%252520Insider.%2526irgwc%253D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclicking%20the%20top%20right-hand%20button%20that%20says%20%26quot%3Bvoucher%26quot%3B%20and%20entering%20your%20email%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20case%20was%20%2479.99%2C%20instead%20of%20its%20current%20sale%20price%20of%20%24179.99%20(its%20traditional%20cost%20is%20listed%20at%20%24264).%20This%20promo%20varies%20a%20bit%20depending%20on%20how%20many%20bottles%20are%20in%20the%20box%20%E2%80%94%20my%20colleague%20redeemed%20a%20%2450%20voucher%20for%20six%20bottles%20of%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn-person%2C%20the%20wines%20are%20good.%20I%20was%20satisfied%20and%20even%20a%20little%20surprised%20by%20their%20quality%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20received%20%24100%20off%20lots%20of%20wine.%20The%20affordable%20bottles%20were%20what%20you'd%20call%20%26quot%3Beasy%20drinking%26quot%3B%20wines%20%E2%80%94%20none%20that%20were%20bold%20and%20weird%20and%20revelatory%20%E2%80%94%20but%20perfect%20for%20casual%20drinking.%20Naked%20Wines%20hit%20the%20%26quot%3Bweekday%20wine%26quot%3B%20niche%20perfectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20would%20stress%20is%20that%20if%20you%20have%20any%20difficulty%20with%20your%20shipment%2C%20or%20you%20don't%20like%20a%20wine%2C%20you%20should%20contact%20Nakedwines.com%20for%20help.%20My%20experiences%20with%20them%20were%20as%20a%20consumer%20rather%20than%20a%20reporter%2C%20and%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20their%20easygoing%20willingness%20to%20make%20sure%