quot%3B%2C%20which%20journalist%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20brought%20to%20light%20through%20his%20publication%2C%20'Satya%20Prakash'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharaj%20libel%20case%20was%20a%20big%20win%20for%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20who%20exposed%20wrongdoing%20in%20the%20Vallabhacharya%20sect.%20He%20was%20praised%20across%20India%20for%20his%20courage%2C%20and%20given%20the%20nickname%20of%20%E2%80%9CLuther%E2%80%9D%2C%20after%20Martin%20Luther%20King%2C%20for%20challenging%20corruption%20in%20religious%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20while%20he%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20publicly%20praised%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20for%20his%20bravery%20and%20dedication%20to%20social%20reform.%20In%20a%20blog%20post%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20acknowledged%20Mr%20Mulji's%20contributions%20and%20highlighted%20his%20commitment%20to%20truth%20and%20justice%2C%20reported%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film's%20narrative%2C%20centred%20on%20the%20sensitive%20event%2C%20drew%20objections%20from%20followers%20of%20the%20Vaishnavite%20Pustimargi%20sect%2C%20dedicated%20to%20God%20Shree%20Krishna%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20The%20followers%20argued%20that%20the%20film%20could%20distort%20their%20religious%20practices%20and%20provoke%20animosity.%20They%20moved%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%2C%20citing%20potential%20violations%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%2C%202021%2C%20and%20self-regulation%20norms%20for%20OTT%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECourt's%20decision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20decided%20to%20stay%20the%20release%20of%20'%3Cem%3EMaharaj%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20pending%20further%20hearings.%20The%20court%20focused%20on%20the%20need%20to%20balance%20artistic%20expression%20with%20communal%20harmony%20and%20address%20concerns%20about%20potential%20religious%20sensitivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20sparked%20debates%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20hashtags%20like%20'BoycottNetflix'%20trending%20among%20users%20who%20are%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20content%20of%20the%20film.%20Legal%20experts%20have%20talked%20about%20the%20ongoing%20tensions%20between%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20respect%20for%20religious%20beliefs%20in%20Indian%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718390460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5p2gsf8o_-jaideep_625x300_29_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-controversy-over-netflix-film-maharaj-starring-aamir-khan-son-junaid-khan-5890277%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20has%20temporarily%20halted%20the%20release%20of%20'Maharaj'%2C%20a%20Netflix%20film%20starring%20Aamir%20Khan's%20son%20Junaid%20Khan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-controversy-over-netflix-film-maharaj-starring-aamir-khan-son-junaid-khan-5890277%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-controversy-over-netflix-film-maharaj-starring-aamir-khan-son-junaid-khan-5890277%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-controversy-over-netflix-film-maharaj-starring-aamir-khan-son-junaid-khan-5890277%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitanshi%3A%20I%20want%20to%20be%20the%20next%20lady%20SRK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718390200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111005891%2Cimgsize-53206.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Flaapataa-ladies-star-nitanshi-goel-expresses-her-desire-to-become-t