ently%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-to-leave-for-g7-summit-in-italy-today-in-1st-overseas-visit-of-new-term-5881781%5C%22%3EItaly%20for%20the%20G-7%20summit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20many%20layers%20of%20the%202024%20election%20mandate%20are%20still%20unravelling.%20While%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20won%20293%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20bagged%20232%20in%20an%20unexpectedly%20tight%20election%20this%20time.%20The%20BJP%20was%20reduced%20to%20240%20seats%20from%20303%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20almost%20doubled%20its%20tally%20from%2052%20to%2099.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%202024%20Math%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20175%20of%20the%20190%20direct%20contests%20with%20the%20Congress%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2092%25.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20win%20only%2015%20such%20seats%2C%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%208%25.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20faced%20off%20against%20each%20other%20in%20215%20seats.%20Of%20these%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20153%20(a%20drop%20of%2022%20from%20last%20time)%20and%20the%20Congress%2062%20(an%20increase%20of%2047)%2C%20with%20strike%20rates%20of%2071%25%20and%2029%25%2C%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20regional%20parties%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20direct%20contests%20with%20the%20BJP%20had%20totalled%20185%2C%20of%20which%20the%20BJP%20won%20128%2C%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2069%25.%20Regional%20players%20could%20win%2057%2C%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2031%25.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20such%20seats%20was%20reduced%20to%20178.%20Of%20these%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2087%20(a%20drop%20of%2041)%20and%20regional%20parties%2091%20(a%20rise%20of%2034)%2C%20with%20strike%20rates%20of%2049%25%20and%2051%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felection-result-2024-nine-things-that-may-explain-the-2024-mandate-5821774%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20Nine%20Things%20That%20May%20Explain%20the%202024%20Mandate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20of%20the%2063%20seats%20lost%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%202024%2C%20as%20many%20as%2022%20were%20bagged%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%2041%20by%20regional%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seats%20contested%20by%20both%20parties%20this%20time%20can%20broadly%20be%20divided%20into%20three%20categories%20based%20on%20how%20many%20times%20they've%20been%20won%20in%20the%20three%20elections%20since%202009%3A%20stronghold%20seats%20(won%20twice%20or%20thrice)%2C%20battleground%20or%20'moderate'%20seats%20(won%20just%20once)%2C%20and%20difficult%20or%20'weak'%20seats%20(ones%20that%20have%20never%20been%20won%20by%20a%20party).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStronghold%20Seats%20Formed%20A%20Majority%20of%20BJP's%20Tally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20262%20stronghold%20seats%20this%20time%2C%20of%20which%20it%20managed%20to%20retain%20184%2C%20a%20success%20rate%20of%2070%25.%20The%20Congress%20won%2036%20and%20other%20parties%20won%20seven.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%2082%20battleground%20or%20'moderate'%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20a%20success%20rate%20of%2037%25%2C%20winning%2030%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20won%2014%20and%20other%20parties%20won%2038.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOf%20the%20199%20difficult%20or%20'weak'%20seats%2C%20including%20those%20that%20were%20contested%20by%20allies%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2026.%20The%20Congress%20won%2049%20and%20other%20parties%20won%20124.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20184%20wins%20in%20stronghold%20seats%20account%20for%20three-quarters%20of%20the%20BJP's%20total%20tally%20of%20240.%20They%20were%20what%20saved%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStronghold%20Seats%20A%20Third%20Of%20Congress%20Tally%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%20this%20time%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20had%2051%20stronghold%20seats%2C%20of%20which%20it%20could%20retain%2034%2C%20a%20success%20rate%20of%2067%25.%20The%20BJP%20won%2010%2C%20while%20other%20parties%20won%20seven.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOf%20its%C2%A0183%20battleground%20seats%2C%20the%20party%20won%2041%20this%20time.%20Its%20success%20rate%20here%20was%2022%25.%20The%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20won%2093%20and%20other%20parties%20won%2049%20seats.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOf%20the%20309%20seats%20that%20were%20'difficult'%20for%20the%20party%20-%20including%20seats%20that%20were%20contested%20by%20its%20allies%20-%20the%20Congress%20won%2024.%20The%20BJP%20won%20137%20of%20the%20rest%2C%20while%20other%20parties%20got%20148.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%2034%20wins%20in%20stronghold%20seats%20account%20for%20a%20third%20of%20the%20Congress's%20total%20tally%2C%20though%20the%20party%20made%20gains%20in%20moderate%20and%20difficult%20seats%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-verdict-2024-shows-politics-is-now-deeply-personal-for-indians-5857120%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20Verdict%202024%20Shows%20Politics%20Is%20Now%20Deeply%20Personal%20For%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20fascinating%20aspect%20of%20this%20election%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20routed%20in%20most%20direct%20contests%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%202019%2C%20has%20come%20out%20strong%20in%20these%20seats%20this%20time%2C%20winning%20almost%2030%25%20of%20them%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%2C%20among%20others.%20The%20party's%20showing%20has%20shattered%20the%20'invincible'%20image%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20also%20challenged%20the%20notion%20that%20only%20regional%20parties%20can%20defeat%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStronghold%20Seats%20of%20Both%20Congress%20%26amp%3B%20BJP%20Have%20Declined%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20these%20results%2C%20the%20overall%20classification%20of%20seats%20stands%20altered.%20Stronghold%20seats%20(those%20that%20have%20been%20won%20three%20to%20four%20times%20since%202009)%20of%20the%20BJP%20have%20declined%20from%20262%20to%20199%2C%20while%20the%20Congress's%20have%20dropped%20from%2051%20to%2038.%20The%20battleground%20seats%20(won%20twice)%20stand%20at%2093%20and%2054%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20respectively%2C%20while%20difficult%20seats%20(won%20just%20once)%20are%2078%20and%20166.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20there%20are%20173%20seats%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20285%20for%20the%20Congress%20that%20can%20be%20considered%20weak%2C%20that%20is%2C%20they%20have%20never%20been%20won%20since%202009.%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20allocated%20to%20allies%20in%20the%20latest%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718364900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftbgduae8_-bjp-generic-reuters_625x300_04_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-stronghold-seats-saved-the-day-for-bjp-5889526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20most%20fascinating%20aspect%20of%20this%20election%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20routed%20in%20most%20direct%20contests%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%202019%2C%20has%20come%20out%20strong%20this%20time%2C%20winning%20almost%2030%25%20of%20such%20seats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.