n%20the%20country%20and%20around%20the%20world.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20alternatives%20like%20copper%2C%20bamboo%2C%20and%20various%20forms%20of%20wood%20that%20people%20are%20using%20instead%20of%20plastic.%20However%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20these%20alternatives%20have%20their%20own%20drawbacks%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20expensive%20for%20widespread%20use%20and%20tend%20to%20be%20heavyweight.%20These%20issues%20pose%20logistical%20challenges%20for%20manufacturers%20looking%20to%20use%20them%20in%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20decided%20to%20look%20for%20alternatives%20that%20were%20lighter%20in%20weight%20and%20sturdier%20in%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20the%20right%20niche%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20co-founded%20Greenevon%20Bio%20Bottles%20along%20with%20Chintan%20Prajapati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChintan%20joined%20me%20midway%20through%20my%20research.%20While%20I%20was%20confident%20in%20my%20direction%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20concentrate%20solely%20on%20research%20and%20sought%20someone%20who%20could%20effectively%20market%20the%20product.%20Chintan%20was%20the%20perfect%20fit%20for%20this%20role%2C%20and%20our%20responsibilities%20are%20divided%20along%20similar%20lines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20across%20from%20me%2C%20holding%20a%20bottle%20that%20resembled%20a%20typical%20single-use%20plastic%20bottle%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98I%20am%20a%20bottle%20but%20I%20am%20not%20plastic%E2%80%99%20printed%20on%20it%20%E2%80%94%20Nikhil%20is%20confident%20that%20the%20bottle%20will%20decompose%20in%20nature%20within%20six%20months%20or%20180%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20tap%20the%20bottle%2C%20and%20it%20will%20sound%20like%20plastic%3B%20you%20can%20touch%20it%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it%20looks%20identical.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D