ratio%20and%20durability%2C%20and%20can%20also%20be%20made%20transparent.%20The%20combination%20of%20polycarbonate%20from%20the%20plant%20and%20starch%20forms%20the%20raw%20material%20for%20the%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20elaborates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Nikhil%20nearly%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20to%20refine%20the%20bottles%20to%20their%20present%20state.%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20the%20bottles%20can%20be%20moulded%20into%20various%20shapes%2C%20capable%20of%20holding%20both%20liquid%20and%20solid%20foods%2C%20and%20can%20withstand%20different%20temperatures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20stage%20was%20achieved%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20hurdle%20that%20I%20faced%20while%20law%20designing%20these%20bottles%20was%20making%20them%20transparent%20under%20different%20temperatures%20and%20environments.%20The%20material%20reacted%20differently%20to%20the%20sun%2C%20cold%2C%20and%20rain%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20challenge%20to%20stabilise%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Nikhil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bottles%20can%20hold%20liquids%20such%20as%20water%20and%20juices%2C%20semi-liquids%2C%20pharma%20products%2C%20dairy%20products%2C%20as%20well%20as%20solid%20food%20items.%20They%20can%20be%20shaped%20and%20moulded%20in%20any%20form%20such%20as%20containers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20three%20key%20factors%20that%20the%20bottle%20brings%20to%20the%20table%20are%20%E2%80%94%20It%20is%20100%25%20degradable%2C%20it%20is%20stable%20under%2055-degree%20Celsius%20temperatures%2C%20and%20it%20has%20zero%20polycarbonate%20leaking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC0sDR4IyS_i%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagr