ages%20to%20Cities%3A%20How%20Coca-Cola%20Uses%20Coolers%20to%20Transform%20Businesses%20for%20Indian%20Retailers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20sponsored%20by%20Coca-Cola%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20regular%20refrigerator.%20However%2C%20Coca-Cola%E2%80%99s%20coolers%2C%20easily%20recognisable%20by%20their%20red%20and%20white%20design%2C%20stocked%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20beverages%2C%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20common%20in%20India.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20talking%20about%20their%20growing%20visibility%20across%20cities%20but%20through%20the%20towns%20to%20the%20villages%2C%20where%20these%20coolers%20stand%20tall%20in%20kiranas%2C%20hotel%20corners%2C%20or%20retail%20aisles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20vast%20network%20of%20providing%20beverages%20to%20over%205%20million%20outlets%20across%20the%20country%2C%20Coca-Cola%20is%20expanding%20the%20presence%20of%20its%20coolers%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20India.%20With%20India%20achieving%20100%20percent%20electrification%20of%20villages%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekiranas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20fast-growing%20network%20of%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20large%20retailers%20now%20effortlessly%20use%20the%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20as%20part%20of%20their%20shop%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20bringing%20to%20reality%20what%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20former%20president%20Robert%20Woodruff%20famously%20said%20about%20winning%20in%20the%20beverage%20market%20%E2%80%94%20delivering%20its%20products%20%E2%80%9Cwithin%20an%20arm%E2%80%99s%20reach%20of%20desire%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20any%20desire%3A%20The%20desire%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F293356%2Fhealth-benefits-of-kanji-fermented-rice-water-ancient-south-india-food-science%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecool%2C%20refreshing%20beverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20be