2noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F243528%2Fmumbai-best-vada-pav-stall-food-origin-ashok-vaidya-maharashtra-history-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20garlic%3Cem%3E%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20create%20a%20beautiful%20symphony.%20The%20duo%20has%20found%20favour%20in%20Sachin%20Tendulkar.%20As%20he%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3ECurly%20Tales%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20was%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20his%20growing-up%20years.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20hours%20of%20practising%20on%20the%20field%2C%20I%20used%20to%20have%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20the%20canteen%20and%20would%20eat%20four%20to%20five%20of%20them%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20years%20haven%E2%80%99t%20diminished%20the%20love%20it%20seems.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20a%20Marathi%20portal%20in%202011%2C%20Tendulkar%20reiterated%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20and%20my%20son%20(Arjun)%20love%20to%20eat%20%3Cem%3Evada-pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20Shivaji%20Park%20Gymkhana%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20that%20can%20beat%20this%20snack%2C%20laced%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Swati%20Snacks%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20belly%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Tardeo%20lies%20an%20eatery%20that%20has%20stuck%20to%20one%20philosophy%3A%20home%20food%20is%20the%20best%20food.%20Minakshi%20Jhaveri%2C%20a%20single%20mother%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252694%2Fswati-snacks-minakshi-jhaveri-iconic-eatery-india-inspiring-single-mother-success-stories-authentic-homemade-food-chaat-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwati%20Snacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20any%20prior%20business%20acumen%2C%20serving%20four%20items%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Esev%20puri%2C%20bhel%20puri%2C%20ragda%20pattice%20and%20pani%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%2