al%20Achievement%E2%80%99%20in%202020%2C%20and%20Vinati%E2%80%99s%20book%20%E2%80%98East%20or%20West%3A%20An%20NRI%20Mother%E2%80%99s%20Manual%20on%20How%20to%20Bring%20up%20Desi%20Children%20Overseas%E2%80%99%20getting%20global%20acclaim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20family%20may%20now%20be%20settled%20across%20the%20globe%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20Vinati%20lives%20in%20London%2C%20Pavan%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20Mahima%20in%20England%2C%20and%20Ashima%20in%20Seattle%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reverence%20for%20the%20environment%20ties%20them%20together.%20It%20lies%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20everything%20they%20undertake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20the%20O%E2%80%99Land%20Plantation%20is%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20stunning%20landscapes%20and%20the%20desire%20to%20not%20let%20them%20be%20infiltrated%20with%20irresponsible%20tourism%20that%20attracted%20the%20couple%20in%202007%20when%20they%20set%20out%20to%20buy%20the%20land.%20%E2%80%9CPavan%20felt%20that%20if%20we%20purchased%20a%20crucial%20piece%20of%20territory%2C%20which%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F260553%2Fwildlife-conservation-elephants-save-school-teacher-hero-west-bengal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelephant%20corridor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20could%20be%20preserved%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Vinati%20explains.%20Dotted%20with%20tea%20and%20pepper%20plantations%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20responsible%20for%20adding%20to%20this%20lush%20vegetation%20with%20fruit%20trees%2C%20vegetable%20crops%2C%20cloves%2C%20coffee%20and%20other%20spices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20well%20aware%20that%20the%20economics%20of%20organic%20agriculture%20aren%E2%80%99t%20lucrative.%20The%20prices%20did%20not%20justify%20the%20efforts%20they%20were%20putting%20in.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20saw%20this%20as%20our%20chance%20to%20make%20the%20authorities%20wake%20up%20and%20realise%20the%20difficulties%20that%20or